  If I have not nuked, will summoning mobs summon me between pets?  If I pull with malosi or something that does no damage I suspect I might not get summoned.  However, the earth pet will have rooted the mob, so I might.  Anyone have experience soloing summoning mobs and know what will happen?  Chain healing is not as efficient as chain petting. <br>
<br>
  Elfnom<br>
