<br>
Best way to do summoning mobs is bring another mage and duo.  Or use air pet and see how darn good you are at timing when they stun and /pet get lost and new pet in during that stun.  But I'd happen to guess that a mage who did that alot on any summoning creature worth soloing exp wise, probably would have a shorter life expectancy then Archangels in the movie Reign of Fire. <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br>
